    A --> D["Low Impact, Easy to Test"]
    B --> B1["Landing page headline<br/>CTA button color/text<br/>Welcome bonus display"]
    C --> C1["Registration flow redesign<br/>Deposit page overhaul<br/>New payment methods"]
    D --> D1["Font changes<br/>Image swaps<br/>Footer content"]
